insert into `destoon_article_data_21` (`itemid`, `content`) values('718','<p><span>2017年11月26日下午，在西安半坡国际艺术区，由中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会主办、杠杠文创承办的“<span>中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会陕西论坛</span>”<span>隆重举行。</span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAibRM8ApQWY9kbGPicliaeOMIaGL4XBBXzGdXaibic0hyicKHXAIfCYpCa88g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"1000\"  /></p><p><span>陕西论坛“全家福”合影留念</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span>本次论坛以</span>“美育·公益·文创”<span>为主题，邀请到中央电视台著名主持人、中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会主任<strong>杨柳</strong>先生，中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会常务副秘书长兼办公室主任</span></span><strong><span>马凌云</span></strong><span>先生，以及陕西广播电视台播音指导、著名节目主持人<strong>徐杰</strong>先生，半坡国际艺术区杠杠文创创始人</span><strong><span>谢宛居</span></strong><span>先生，西北大学博士生导师<strong>周东华</strong>教授，西安广播电视台主持人<strong>李龙</strong>先生，<strong>景琦</strong>博士，以及在陕优秀播音员主持人代表，陕西高校艺术类学者代表，文化艺术界代表共同莅临本次盛会。</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAGryFqM71386aibxlicB2OknolpibueL6c36Bc65hoRM9yMhqE0Ia4VBsw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-w=\"1280\"  /></p><p><span>著名口哨表演艺术家文艺开场，引人入胜</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbA8zSqa5N3xtGVBTl8508RUC17zzjlXOl1CWibZNYvW3rbTzLyeOHLHjQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"1000\"  /></p><p><span>景琦博士担纲主持，气场全开</span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAIHwGRtZ1m7JvXaK5Nshj4gpJYSug8uUUSHn6ftQTVqh3BHK1Ih7JpQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>现场高朋满座，最右是青春直播，</span><span>点赞过万</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAxkfSfT1dicKfMFqeLVNvkF3pQ59LxESzd1000jwRZXk5txv5OPNtYCw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会主任</span></p><p><span>杨柳先生致开幕词</span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAdpcoylKeea1o782TNbbkASdNciaugWlWyhWwf4tzJFNz2AibYAX5pNNQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>陕西广播电视台著名节目主持人徐杰致辞</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAJzico9eveFvGF8VOzq25GIM4MsMHJ0ogjl2En6VFGiccx65MwyNlsXCw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>半坡国际艺术区杠杠文创创始人谢宛居致辞</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAbDOicyxoSdCDpMOTe9JPY4ibqewtpZgsAibojeGh1ibbeLwTUdwlFfuPWw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6325\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAkjkKIFGmj8yia0XGl5m7GKoKwQtM2PD8gyCicCkfjDSeDPle1MabfXiaQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>群贤毕至，共筑梦想</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAcSaBzTjV5ibqdfgmQwqWS5efD4yBtCcjnkH6VC9PSEE8oUjOHqFTQQw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAat64wQnrMiaKiaibBf1A4KyG1ySApfZL8JkJDukDlgwXR4EkFEwiciaUfNA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbADQqsN70J0K2zQFgAjHwHTuicOyK3ic0uUqNljqtE3GjeJ22xx7Or173Q/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>与会嘉宾现场签名，合影留念</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbANGxV3OEkjz3bgT0v6jcqVeyqjTHXIY6pf56QfAib66RAPNKwkPAyXvA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAV5picNy0d7I3K4YibxfLwm0ibtv3icHyaaia29iaIicicIiavqP0hZRF8rb75bQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbA7ELAljicCP0ULDtNqChzbVAibDkboeXTN0SGbib5NPUVzNfBSPUPbfPew/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.167883211678832\" data-w=\"685\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAdJjvWMwJhglW1nnkaf5k7iaOgibx7ViauIRLeBB6qI7QZVvlB4M75uPLg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAuVpPCxcmmfUAvlIzFiatklPEdlQBzmeb4KDnHrdoXQklEgg0F7DHysQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAGwo8Y4ccDzOUrOEG7SRicErkjDeLU6NUJOsP0UXQbicUH3rQlfFh3YIA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>抽奖环节，不亦乐乎！</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAYLrsPMydJsOWpGT911lnCtv6VdIY9kpdfA7nrYEWdhecicjnrVn4ZZA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4953271028037383\" data-w=\"535\"  /></p><p><span>红酒伴鲜花：精美茶歇，典雅色香味</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAkjdvIzxUOex4yH1wpkFyLibkvHK35CoXLryYkTjUftKVrUVG11MmiaOw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span>同行之间互相交流，暖意融融</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span>首届</span>“陕西论坛”立足于互联网时代播音员主持人所面临的机遇与挑战，以“美育•公益•文创”为主题深入探讨了如何在互联网+时代聚力社会力量构筑在陕主持人的精神家园，实现播音员、主持人社会影响力的互联网传播，践行公益，并在实践中传承文化经典、传播正能量，以网为媒创造新时代的文化繁荣！</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JK33VBiaLLdThDrmBOfKXKsia6AWE9fgbAgYpzE5sQr2kAFqO3Cict5mic8A2SA6OEwYJ3BKQsITmX9RgmT8GicyllQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-w=\"800\"  /></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span>除了丰盛的文化大餐，现场还准备了丰富的抽奖环节和精致的西点美酒，在冬日的暖阳下，伴随着动听的音乐，与会者中不仅有收获大奖的幸运者，论坛主办方还为每位到场嘉宾提供了由杠杠文创友情制作的设计师原创艺术品伴手礼。</span> </span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>“中华文化促进会主持人专业委员会陕西论坛”在发自肺腑、干货满满的主题演讲和媒体同仁的亲切交流中落下帷幕，但构筑在陕主持人精神家园、推动美育教育、践行公益的美好梦想才刚刚开启，期待陕西论坛能够秉持开放、包容、聚力、创新的发展理念，打造属于在陕主持人的美好时代！</span></p><p><span></span> </p><p><span><span>编辑：高源</span></span></p>          <p><strong  >愿</strong>我们都能<strong  >找到</strong>自己<strong  >心中所爱</strong></p><p>勇敢去爱、坚持去做</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>欢迎<strong  >关注</strong>我们这个<strong  >有爱的公众号</strong></p><p>小e会定期更新<strong  >与主持相关</strong>的内容</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>让我们因“声”相遇，因“声”结缘</p><p>我们在这里，等你<img class=\"__bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.7246376811594203\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JK33VBiaLLdRXSMRLIWCaNnt4KHCEoSPiaqUCDjRz7ctvzSyBQloKHHL7ibXlmE9kqSyfQxAPK1AbUCSpIvfx7zPQ/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1242\"   width=\"auto\"  /></p>   <p> </p>');
insert into `destoon_article_data_21` (`itemid`, `content`) values('719','<p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.15625\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/lCn1Q1r0xBWfgxgzt8SmyQZAhnibVhtLKFFlU0t7qL44yW5yV4Gcs5MmmZQOPHX7ibIU3SCA1ngK1FsRfrYiaeHMg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\"   width=\"auto\"  /></p><p> </p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyV8jqGDykA04ITgGG0dbiblGcWA1bqgwjsCgJNAevvoNXkflfG7Xls4CA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.943359375\" data-w=\"1024\"  /></p>   <p> </p><p> </p><p>&nbsp; 今天，美育在三坊七巷的奥乐斯亲子厨房举办了11月的生日会~这次参加的是我们美育10月，11月生日的学员，小编在这里<strong><span>祝小天使们生日快乐！祝愿小天使们幸福快乐的长大~</span></strong> </p><p> </p><p><img data-type=\"gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVeOQRLJmOZ2gMibTBbxuXRrdibEkubju7pZzLaQRV0KWNzDRicEygRwMRQ/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3861003861003861\" data-w=\"259\"  /></p><p> </p><p>今天小寿星们在奥乐斯亲子厨房要DIY的甜品是推推乐吔！色彩诱人的推推乐，好有趣又好玩的动手过程，快快跟小编一起来围观吧！</p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVPdIg6PJq5zG7mia5VBSEy7RRImS9CFjKtCibVejOBD1WBYw8ibAC4oyew/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-w=\"640\"  /></p><p><span></span> </p><p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>1</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p><p><span>大家先和奥乐斯亲子厨房的老师一起玩开场小游戏！</span></p><p><span>一起蹦蹦跳跳，摇摇小胳膊，扭扭小屁股！</span></p><p><img data-type=\"gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyV9Vj2CbXtAsEDGhRsSVHw8Pz3ibAicicNsq1xR2b8Tx1H7Fuqm93ao7avA/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0718954248366013\" data-w=\"153\"  /></p><p> </p><p> </p>      <p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVhtE6RtnnCkgp5DlFDNiadm0Yib4CHoMwgZRSiac901JmjjKAjwnlc5RNA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4975922953451044\" data-w=\"623\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>2</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p>      <p><span>当然啦，在开始DIY 之前，洗洗小手是重要的一步啦~</span></p><p><span>我们都是爱干净讲卫生的好宝宝哦~</span> </p><p> </p>      <p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVRsGACOzp1ecgBBicFAbplEDhVOqdSzamSicRwZCUmIyZJwyn3buDDYBg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6650390625\" data-w=\"1024\"  /></p><p> </p>   <p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>3</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p><p><span>我们一起来叠冰淇淋！看谁叠的高！</span> </p><p><span> </span></p>   <p> </p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVjL3ict5zX3aj4E5GBdjKYRCfoiaoY5nLGE5fTO4PibxsqrEobLBSM7GOQ/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6691358024691358\" data-w=\"810\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>4</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p><p><span>要准备开始了，看看每个小朋友听得有多么的认真呀~</span></p><p> </p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVicGpUiaW2eM0wbHSVUM3alsmBGvKzoNujicLpzaiaicT7IvEYn5XCBNI0yQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4991762767710048\" data-w=\"607\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVLrkN03UYDezNbPYmbjH5v7dbE2aT1nc5amw2iclvLqJC0381mw6kYQA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"497\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>5</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p>      <p><span>哇哇哇！要开始动手啦~小盆友和家长齐上阵！</span></p><p><span>小编非常的期待成品呢！</span> </p><p><span> </span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyV5TttUAPxgPqprStWo6vej9jWmrhOPDQDqSIDg14QfpOKeN5XflbM7w/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4942339373970346\" data-w=\"607\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVNKs1lPia2tQAS83YmZgs31vgS0licAP98bfia0sRQcNAmMyRTwRGSrq4g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5074380165289256\" data-w=\"605\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>6</p></span>       <p> </p>      <p><span>快来看！快来看！是不是棒棒哒~ </span></p><p><span>小编看了都要流口水啦</span></p><p> </p>      <p><if<em></em>rame class=\"video_if<em></em>rame\" data-vidtype=\"2\" allowfullscreen=\"\" f<em></em>rameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-w=\"272\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/if<em></em>rame/preview.html?vid=k13281s130f&amp;width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0\"></if<em></em>rame> </p><p> </p>          <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>7</p></span>    <p> </p>   <p> </p>      <p><span>趁着把做好的推推乐拿去冷藏的时间，小朋友们一起玩起了弹珠游戏和扔球游戏！好欢乐呀~大家都玩得不亦乐乎！</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyV9gVaFuIwyA2A2rLjlB9iammJicunIJAWv93hseyIbxErgA3cluL4HxzA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"497\"  /></p><p><span></span> </p><p><span></span></p><p> </p><p> </p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVY0wjNDAINE5oVvP5GfGJZ8qY2DZg5TuO38TNpPvzIibfZBP9pbNZnRw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-copyright=\"0\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5099667774086378\" data-w=\"602\"  /></p><p><span></span> </p><p><span> </span></p>   <p> </p>    <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>8</p></span>    <p> </p>   <p> </p>      <p><span>玩完游戏就要点蜡烛许愿切蛋糕啦！</span> </p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVvGa0E1NdxrpEQPK9gWq3z95hF3HCyj24egCibBNWq584dicZBV4deNGA/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334814814814815\" data-w=\"675\"  /></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyV6SFnia04GcSph41QaZUuwsjfqbfaR5ibudYX1olE55aRtDiaic5PLD9H3g/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5175879396984924\" data-w=\"597\"  /></p><p><span>一边吃着生日蛋糕，一边品尝自己动手做的推推乐，</span></p><p><span>好幸福哇~</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVIMXhw69K27PDFib4UiaGb0uuDzctjGn2SDKjhxakc501TjSvUCpEdBcw/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9024390243902439\" data-w=\"820\"  /></p><p><span></span> </p>   <p> </p><p> </p>       <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>9</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p>      <p><span>美育老师们不仅给宝贝们在生活里<strong><span>带来仪式感</span></strong>的同时，</span></p><p><strong><span>学会感恩也是重要的一项</span></strong><span>！</span></p><p><span>抱抱亲爱的妈妈~您辛苦啦！</span> </p><p><span> </span></p>      <p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVUbJQpibSpJSDJHPT9u1b52WhDc1Zuich2VoD8ZztHfZzu6yZX3TyD73A/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6687116564417178\" data-w=\"815\"  /></p>   <p> </p>   <p> </p>    <span></span><span></span>  <span><p>00</p></span><span></span>       <p> </p>      <p><span>集体大合照！</span> </p><p><span> </span></p>   <p> </p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lCn1Q1r0xBUowAWkIRjMZRKJib1SGAicyVbtkvkLibgNECU2QaibFP2XKGS2QRTjmzy0uahuRUlhSQwSKCOwtdKwrA/0?wx_fmt=png\"   class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6801470588235294\" data-w=\"816\"  /></p><p> </p>      <p><span>…… </span></p><p><span></span></p><p><img data-type=\"gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/