><p> </p><p><img class=\"__bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Y8sGn3sLicIWXgJQ2vDLkK0KVicGhL8hVicPtKmwmcBsbvfIfhwHOicWibSGS870ibaM4bfwEVQDpqEQQZV2vRXzSU3A/0?\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"22\"   width=\"auto\"  /></p><p><span>涂鸦时间</span></p><p><span>周二至周五 14:00--20:00</span></p><p><span>周六、周日 &nbsp;9:00--17:30</span></p><p><span>（周一公休）</span></p>      <p> </p>        <p><span>添加</span><span>“晟蓝小秘书”</span><span><span>为</span><span>微信好友</span></span> </p><p><span>有疑问随时解决，</span><span>约课更方便</span></p><p><span>我在等你哦!</span></p><p><span><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.06875\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Y8sGn3sLicIX3UjQNmVuZIMiaBaqCKVwrptz8qIKx6BZ96F4LN03medo6fGccsbia9FDooyYZ7vBBMdRO0aP0Tsrg/640?\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\"   width=\"auto\"  /></span></p><p><span>识别二维码，加我为好友</span></p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Y8sGn3sLicIWnpaKlHkLJOIdfXzcn84AdKWahTvia5vlWra41oJkC5cDNpyHgcd4d7zedIh9WjIQeZG3XD0k7Knw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"270\" height=\"197\"   width=\"198\"  /></p><p><span><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.06875\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Y8sGn3sLicIX3UjQNmVuZIMiaBaqCKVwrptz8qIKx6BZ96F4LN03medo6fGccsbia9FDooyYZ7vBBMdRO0aP0Tsrg/640?\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\"   width=\"auto\"  /></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span>关注</span><span><span></span><span><span>晟</span><span>蓝</span><span>少</span><span>儿</span><span>画</span><span>院</span><span>公众号</span></span></span></p><p><span>更多精彩活动内容等您来看</span> <span></span></p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.06875\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Y8sGn3sLicIX3UjQNmVuZIMiaBaqCKVwrptz8qIKx6BZ96F4LN03medo6fGccsbia9FDooyYZ7vBBMdRO0aP0Tsrg/640?\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\"   width=\"auto\"  /></p><p><span>长按二维码 &nbsp;关注公众号</span></p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Y8sGn3sLicIXnTY4ZDMe98n43fxXFDdrW8fBNcQycHpgicpuYQicVWxX